flowchart TD
  A[Sensor Read] --> B[Build payload envelope]
  B --> C[Include required fields\nimei, project_id, msgid, packet_type, ts/timestamp]
  C --> D["MQTT PUBLISH\nIMEI/heartbeat"]
  D --> E{Ack received?}
  E -->|Yes| F[Continue sampling loop]
  E -->|No| G[Retry publish with backoff]
  G --> D

  subgraph Server Side
    S1[Broker ACL validates topic] --> S2[Go subscriber ingests]
    S2 --> S3[Transform + validate\nDNA/schema + strict checks]
    S3 --> S4[Persist telemetry + update shadow/hot cache]
    S4 --> S5[Rules/alerts/actions]
  end

  D -.-> S1
